        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Bug Fixes</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed external monitor support — Scani now correctly scans whichever screen your cursor is on</li>
                    <li>Fixed overlay appearing on wrong screen in multi-monitor setups</li>
                    <li>Fixed screenshot showing only partial screen on external displays</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
