        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Languages, Custom Hotkeys &amp; Auto-Updates</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added Korean, Japanese, Chinese (Simplified &amp; Traditional), German, Spanish, French, Italian, Russian OCR support</li>
                    <li>Set a custom key combination to trigger scans in Settings</li>
                    <li>Automatic updates via Sparkle</li>
                    <li>Added QR Code and Barcode Scan Support so you can Search or Copy QR code/Barcode links</li>
                    <li>Improved text selection — larger hit area on handles</li>
                    <li>Bug fixes</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <pubDate>Thu, 22 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
